  "original_title": "\u2019\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'People's opinions should be respected'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Christian Council of Sri Lanka has requested the members of Parliament to respect the opinions of the people.",
        "It has also been emphasized that an all-party government should be formed immediately to take care of the situation and propose solutions to recover from the state of corruption in the country.",
        "The National Christian Council of Sri Lanka has also stated that it is very concerned about the current situation in the country.",
        "Further, a warning has also been given that the current situation is seen to be heading towards a political disaster beyond the country's fractious situation. (a)"
      ],
